SUMMARY:Wednesday Wellness Webinar: Push Pause on People Pleasing
LOCATION:Tampa \, FL United States
DESCRIPTION:Respect and honesty are essential to positive relationships. H
 owever\, healthy boundaries that define appropriate physical and emotional
  limits are crucial for self-care and positive connections. Join this webi
 nar to learn how to identify and set healthy boundaries with your relation
 ships. This presentation does count towards your Wellness Incentive benefi
 ts - 100 Wednesday May 27\, 2026  12  1PM Click here to register or scan t
 he QR code \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/187481
